_json.gridTitle: Pesto chicken stew with cheesy dumplings
_json.description: Pesto chicken stew with cheesy dumplings- Ingredients      2 tbsp olive oil     12-15 chicken thighs, skin removed, bone in     200g smoked bacon lardons or chopped bacon     1 large onion, chopped     4 celery sticks, chopped     3 leeks, chopped     4 tbsp plain flour     200ml white wine     1l chicken stock     2 bay leaves     200g frozen peas          140g fresh pesto     small bunch basil, chopped  For the dumplings      140g butter     250g self-raising flour     100g parmesan, grated     50g pine nuts
